flowchart TD
    A[Packet Arrives] --> B{IPv4?}
    B -->|No| C[XDP_PASS]
    B -->|Yes| D[Extract Source IP]
    D --> E[Get Current Time]
    E --> F{State Exists?}
    F -->|No| G["Create State\ncount = 1"]
    G --> C
    F -->|Yes| H{Window Expired?}
    H -->|Yes| I["Reset Window\ncount = 1"]
    I --> C
    H -->|No| J{Count >= Limit?}
    J -->|Yes| K[XDP_DROP]
    J -->|No| L[Increment Count]
    L --> C
